<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٩١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3340">‌الْمَسْعُودِيُّ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6778">‌وَبْرَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6736">‌هَمَّامِ بْنِ الْحَارِثِ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">‌عَبْدُ اللهِ </a>: <span class="c2">«إِنَّ مِنَ السُّنَّةِ الْغُسْلَ يَوْمَ الْجُمُعَةِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>